WEBVTT

00:08:59.170 --> 00:09:02.055
because what she wanted
to remind people of

00:09:03.468 --> 00:09:05.567
was that this

00:09:05.591 --> 00:09:06.782
is what it was like

00:09:07.813 --> 00:09:10.984
in the 1950s

00:09:11.008 --> 00:09:13.725
trying to be black in America

00:09:13.749 --> 00:09:16.087
and fight for your rights.

00:09:16.561 --> 00:09:20.068
During the year, a little over a year,
that the boycott lasted,

00:09:21.298 --> 00:09:23.927
there were over four church bombings.

00:09:23.951 --> 00:09:26.955
Martin Luther King's house
was bombed twice.

00:09:27.392 --> 00:09:30.865
Other civil rights leaders' houses
were bombed in Birmingham.